               <note type="description">A gathering of metaphysical and theological questions presented in an analytical and doctrinal form. (OY)</note>
               <note type="biblioComments">OY lists 18 mss, but has unfortunately conflated three separate works that contain masāʾil: K. al-maʿrifa (Carullah 986, Shehit Ali 1341, Carullah 2080, 22b, Fatih 5322, Veliyuddin 1821, Azhar 33595); ʿAqīdat ahl al-ikhtiṣāṣ (3rd profession of faith extract from Fut.I.41–47; Shehit Ali 1342, 145-146b, copied by al-Hamawayh d. 658H; ); a later collection of masāʾil from different authors including IA called K. al-Masāʾil (Esad Ef. 1477, 71-147, Carullah 2120). Maurizio Marconi has analysed all the extant mss and is preparing a critical edition of 54 masāʾil of K. al-Maʿrifa.</note>
